Company Description by the company:
Specialized Products, Ltd. is committed to meeting or exceeding our customer's expectations by utilizing our empowered workforce for all of your wire harness, cable assembly, mechanical assembly, over molding and machining needs, while abiding by UL, CSA, RoHS, and ISO Regulations.

We are committed to satisfy customer needs by:

- A complete understanding of the customer requirements;

- Creating product according to these requirements;

- Meeting or exceeding the requirements during every process cycle; and

- Controlling processes with tools and techniques that allow Specialized Products, Ltd. and its suppliers to improve the system and achieve sustainable growth.
